      "role": "user",
      "content": "ibuprofen is for pain tho right? did u mean an antibiotic pill? also do i really need to call the doctor right away if it's just a tiny bit of yellow stuff? im thinking of just doing the compress and neosporin for a couple days first to see if it settles down before making a whole thing out of it. seems fine if it clears up fast.",
