      "content": "i dont have a prescription for amoxicillin or anything like that lol. can i just buy some of that antibiotic stuff at the chemist? and how much of it should i take to make sure the infection goes away? i'd rather just fix it at home so i dont have to go back to the clinic and pay for another appointment.",
